section.page.pageOne
  h2 Collection demo

  p Intelligently rendering collections can be a bit tricky. 

  p <a href="https://github.com/henrikjoreteg/human-view">HumanView's</a> <code>renderCollection()</code> method makes it simple.

  p The only code required to manage the collection is:

  pre
    code
        | this.renderCollection(
        |    this.collection, 
        |    PersonView, 
        |    this.$('.people')[0]
        | );

  h3 People container:
  div(role="people-list")

  p Try it by clicking the buttons

  .buttons
    button.btn.reset .reset()
    button.btn.fetch .fetch()
    button.btn.shuffle .shuffle()
    button.btn.add Generate Random Person

  p Events are always managed so you don't get any leaks.
